lt\",\"moduleclass_sfx\":\"\",\"cache\":\"1\",\"cache_time\":\"900\",\"cachemode\":\"static\"}',0,'*'),(151,0,'Contact Details','','<ul>\r\n  <li>Grunge Template Inc.</li>\r\n  <li>133 Hydrax Business Estate</li>\r\n  <li>Seattle, WA, 54868</li>\r\n  <li>United States of America</li>\r\n</ul>',2,'footer-c',0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',1,'mod_custom',1,1,'{\"prepare_content\":\"1\",\"backgroundimage\":\"\",\"layout\":\"_:default\",\"moduleclass_sfx\":\"\",\"cache\":\"1\",\"cache_time\":\"900\",\"cachemode\":\"static\"}',0,'*'),(152,0,'Customize the Design with Ease','','<p>We provide <strong>Adobe&reg; Fireworks</strong> PNG image sources with every template, inclusive of a separate source for the logo. This allows for virtually complete customization control over the images that constitute the template..</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"readon\" href=\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=55&amp;Itemid=161\"><span>Read More</span></a></p>',2,'bottom-a',0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',1,'mod_custom',1,1,'{\"prepare_content\":\"1\",\"backgroundimage\":\"\",\"layout\":\"_:default\",\"moduleclass_sfx\":\"\",\"cache\":\"1\",\"cache_time\":\"900\",\"cachemode\":\"static\"}',0,'*'),(153,0,'Module Positions','','<p>The template has 68 collapsible positions, allowing for a multitude of many different layout options.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"readon\" href=\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=50&amp;Itemid=156\"><span>Read More</span></a></p>',2,'bottom-b',0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',1,'mod_custom',1,1,'{\"prepare_content\":\"1\",\"backgroundimage\":\"\",\"layout\":\"_:default\",\"moduleclass_sfx\":\"\",\"cache\":\"1\",\"cache_time\":\"900\",\"cachemode\":\"static\"}',0,'*'),(154,0,'RokStories Placeholder','','<div class=\"rokstories-layout2\">\r\n<div class=\"feature-block\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"images/stories/demo/frontpage/showcase1.jpg\" alt=\"